<h2>Salam Park Riyadh: Visitor Guide &amp; Travel Tips</h2>
<p>Salam Park is one of Riyadh''s oldest and best-loved public parks, built around a large artificial lake in the Al Malaz district. With shaded walking paths, paddle boats, and wide lawns, it remains a favourite evening spot for families looking for an affordable, relaxed outing close to the city centre.</p>
