<h2>Tips</h2><ul><li>Boulevard World''s programming is strongest during Riyadh Season, roughly October to February — check what''s running before you go</li><li>Book headline concert or show tickets well in advance, as popular acts sell out quickly</li><li>Arrive early on weekend evenings to beat both the crowds and the queues for rides</li><li>Combine with Boulevard City next door for dining before or after the main event</li></ul>
<h2>How to Get There</h2><p>Boulevard World sits just off King Fahd Road, close to KAFD and Olaya. <strong>Airport Travel Taxis</strong> offers fixed-price transfers from the airport and all Riyadh hotels, with late-night pickups available after shows. <a href="/booking">Book your transfer</a></p>',
